{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_02_01",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 02 01",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――瑠依と優がグループを組んでから、数週間が過ぎた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several weeks have passed since Rui and Yu formed a group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 3.534072875976563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "1、2、3、4……天動さん走り過ぎよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One‚ two‚ three‚ four… You’re running ahead‚ Tendo-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "呼吸揃えるのを忘れないで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t forget to synchronize your breathing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.266666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ！　分かりました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Understood!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.586666674415271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 12.655442209045093
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――彼女達のレッスンは、個人の実力アップから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The objective of their lessons shifted from individual skill improvement",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.655442209045093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "グループとしての表現力アップに目的が変化していた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to improving their expressiveness as a group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.722108875711758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 20.288775542378424
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……天動さんは一人だけで先走り過ぎだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Tendo-san‚ you’re getting ahead of yourself‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.088775542378425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "鈴村さんはまだまだ遠慮しがちね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and Suzumura-san‚ you’re still being too hesitant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.65544220904509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 24.65544220904509
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 28.266287749881545
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "いや～……ズバッと痛いところ突いてくるなぁ\n協調性は大事にせなあかんよねぇ、瑠・依・ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ouch… She’s really hitting where it hurts\nWe gotta value teamwork‚ right‚ Ru-i-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.99962108321488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 35.232954416548225
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 37.86628774988155
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……からかわないで、マジメにやってよ\nだいたい鈴村さんだって――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Stop teasing me and be serious.\nAnd besides‚ Suzumura-san‚ you’re――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.599621083214885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 42.63634168961517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "だーかーらー\nいつになったら名前で呼んでくれるん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m say-ing\nwhen will ya start calling me by my name?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.83634168961516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 47.569675022948495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……こっちの勝手でしょう？\n苗字で呼ぶ方が好きなのよ、私",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s… my choice‚ isn’t it?\nI like calling you by your last name.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.33634168961515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……はぁ。まあ、グループ仲は勝手に深めて頂戴",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sigh. Well‚ you two can work on your group bonding on your own time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.26300826727222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 53.29634160060553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "じゃあもう一回、通しでやってみましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ let’s try it again from the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.89634160060555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はいっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.99626425749432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 63.86293092416096
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 64.12959759082764
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "は～……今日もめっちゃ疲れたなぁ～\nコーチ、スパルタ過ぎやって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… I’m so tired today\nThe coach is way too strict…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.16293092416096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 71.92572869294752
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……？\nそうだったかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…?\nWas she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 74.38392592900861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "もう、そういう所やん。みんながみんな\n瑠依ちゃんみたいに出来る訳やないんよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See‚ that’s what I’m talking about. Not everyone\ncan do it like you‚ Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.71725926234195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 80.93415405649677
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "人それぞれ、出来ることと出来ひんことがある\n出来へんことがあるから、頑張って練習してるんやんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone has things they’re good at and things they’re not good at.\nWe practice hard because we have things we’re not good at‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8674873898301,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "もう少し、そういうもんなんやって\n知ってくれたら嬉しいなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d be happy if you could understand\nthat a little bit more~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.80082072316344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 93.66748738983011
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……そう、なのかな\n確かに、周りの人のこと、今まで見えてなかったかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is that so?\nI guess I haven’t really been paying attention to the people around me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.00082072316344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 101.46748738983011
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "これからはもう少し、柔軟に考えるようにしてみる\n…………ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll try to be more flexible from now on.\n…………Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.70082072316345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 106.78860675269102
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、瑠依ちゃん\n今うちにデレよったなぁ？　ふふふぅ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Rui-chan.\nYou were just soft with me‚ weren’t ya? Fufufu~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.68860675269106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 112.15925180796523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、デレてなんて……\nって、なんで近づいてくるのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I wasn’t being soft…\nHey‚ why are you coming closer?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.99258514129863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 116.98157001954523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "グループ仲を深めるためのスキンシップでも\nしよう思ってなぁ～……ふふふっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought we could have some skinship\nto deepen our group bond~… Fufufu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.9149033528786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 122.98554016572443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "もう……そういうのはいいから\nバカなこと考えてないで、早く着替えるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on… That’s enough of that.\nStop thinking about stupid things and get changed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.01887349905772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 128.42769039762806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "……あ！　このままやとボイスレッスン遅刻やん！\n瑠依ちゃん、早よ着替えんと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah! We’re gonna be late for our vocal lesson if we don’t hurry!\nRui-chan‚ get changed quickly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.92769039762817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanlocker-00-noon.webp",
